        "title": "Harden Control UI auth, status warnings, and build provenance",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Harden Control UI serving with security headers/CSP and authenticated bootstrap config.\n- Prefer fragment-token handoff, strip URL token material after bootstrap, and document the `?token=` deprecation plan.\n- Render assistant media through authenticated blob fetches instead of reusable tokenized preview URLs, with CSP support for managed blob media.\n- Add Slack/channel health fields and mode-aware warnings for disconnected, stale transport, readback mismatch/error, and missing history/readback scopes.\n- Add build provenance metadata to the bootstrap payload and Debug view.\n- Add deterministic Control UI checksum generation and wire checksum artifacts into CI/release workflows.\n- Add browser smoke coverage for auth bootstrap, token stripping, channel health, Slack warnings, CSP, and basic accessibility checks.\n\n## Validation\n\n- `corepack pnpm test -- ui/src/ui/control-ui-smoke.browser.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/test-projects.mjs src/gateway/control-ui.http.test.ts extensions/slack/src/channel.test.ts extensions/slack/src/monitor/message-handler/preview-finalize.test.ts extensions/slack/src/scopes.test.ts ui/src/ui/chat/grouped-render.test.ts ui/src/ui/controllers/control-ui-bootstrap.test.ts ui/src/ui/views/channels.test.ts src/infra/control-ui-build-provenance.test.ts test/scripts/control-ui-checksums.test.ts src/channels/account-snapshot-fields.test.ts src/plugin-sdk/status-helpers.test.ts test/scripts/ui.test.ts src/gateway/control-ui-csp.test.ts`\n- `corepack pnpm check:changed`\n- `git diff --check`\n\n## Notes\n\n- Gateway assistant-media query-token compatibility is intentionally retained for older Control UI/media links and paired-device compatibility until a release-window removal can be scheduled.\n- Local `gh` CLI is not installed; this PR was opened via the GitHub connector and final ready-for-review transition used GitHub GraphQL after the connector ready mutation hit a response-shape bug.",
